				<p>In particular, the Company adheres to the Personal Information Protection and Electronic Documents Act (PIPEDA), the Alberta Personal Information Protection Act (PIPA), and any other applicable federal, provincial, or territorial laws governing the collection, use, disclosure, and protection of Personal Information. These laws establish the regulatory framework within which the Company processes Personal Information and provide Users with legal rights concerning their privacy and data security.</p>
